## Critical: slugifyCategory Differences

**Property & Dentists** replace `&` with `and`:
```
"Section 24 & Tax Relief" → "section-24-and-tax-relief"
"VAT & compliance" → "vat-and-compliance"
```

**Solicitors** strips `&` entirely:
```
"SRA Compliance & Trust Accounting" → "sra-compliance-trust-accounting"
"VAT & Compliance" → "vat-compliance"
```

**Medical** does not use category slugs in URLs (flat /blog/{slug}).

## Blog Post Front Matter

Markdown files in `{Site}/web/content/blog/*.md`:
```yaml
title: "Post Title"
slug: "post-slug"
canonical: "https://domain/blog/[category-slug/]slug"
metaTitle: "SEO Title | Brand"         # MUST be under 60 chars
metaDescription: "Description"         # MUST be under 155 chars
category: "Category Name"
date: "2026-04-01"
author: "Brand Editorial Team"
image: ""
altText: "Alt text for images"
h1: "Page Heading"
summary: "Brief summary"
schema: ""
faqs:
  - question: "..."
    answer: "..."
```

## Key Files Per Site

- `niche.config.json` — loaded by web via `src/config/niche-loader.ts` (import from `../../../niche.config.json`)
- `src/lib/blog.ts` — getAllPosts(), getPostBySlug(), slugifyCategory(), getCategorySlug()
- `src/lib/schema.ts` — buildBlogPostingJsonLd(), buildOgImageUrl() (Person author, dynamic OG images)
- `src/lib/local-business-schema.ts` — buildLocalBusinessJsonLd() for location pages
- `src/app/blog/[category]/[slug]/page.tsx` — blog post pages (Property/Dentists/Solicitors)
- `src/app/blog/[slug]/page.tsx` — blog post pages (Medical only)
- `src/app/blog/{category-slug}/page.tsx` — category hub pages (static, one per category)
- `src/app/locations/[slug]/page.tsx` — location pages with LocalBusiness schema
- `src/app/api/og/route.tsx` — dynamic OG image generation (edge runtime, branded per site)
- `src/app/robots.ts` — robots.txt generation (includes AI crawler rules)
- `src/middleware.ts` — redirects for old flat /blog/{slug} URLs to /blog/{category}/{slug}
- `web/public/llms.txt` — AI discoverability file (site description, key pages, categories)

