## Python Pipeline

Each site's `pipeline/` folder contains blog generation scripts. They use `config_supabase.py` which adds the repo root to `sys.path` to import `shared_supabase_config.py`. The `OUTPUT_MD_DIR` paths are relative to the script location, pointing to `../web/content/blog/`.

## Year/Tax Year Conventions

- UK tax year: 6 April to 5 April (e.g. "2026/27" = 6 April 2026 to 5 April 2027)
- "2026/26" is INVALID — never use this format
- Tax year topics (self-assessment, pension, tax rates, allowances): use "2026/27"
- Calendar year topics (MTD deadline, VAT registration threshold): use "2026"
- Evergreen topics (how to choose an accountant): no year needed
